image.characterName: モブ HK_筋肉おやじ（大）01-1

parameters: ストーリー　セレナ売ります
\n< Serena >
Now, adventurer. I'd like to ask you something. \n< Man >
Do you understand what you have done? \n< Man >
I did the right thing. \n< Serena >
I see. \n< Man >
An unsuitable job has been assigned to an unsuitable
person. \n< Man >
Accidents do happen, just like that. \n< Man >
Big damage. It's a big loss. \n< Man >
The total debt held by the women who ran away amounts
to 58,000 S. \n< Man >
The opportunity loss caused by the recent incident
amounts to about 300,000 S. \n< Man >
In addition, you have an obligation to pay a penalty
of 800,000 S as a breach of the first, third, and
fourth provisions. \n< Man >
The total is 1,103,800 S. Taking into account the
future losses that this matter will bring to the
guild, your debt to the guild has now increased to
Any objections? \n< Man >
Not there. \n< Serena >
Oh? \n< Man >
I did what I was supposed to do. I have nothing to be
ashamed of. \n< Serena >
You should do what you must do. That's what fairness
is about. \n< Serena >
Do you have a plan to repay such a large amount of
money on your own? \n< Man >
Not at the moment. Unfortunately, no. \n< Serena >
Of course, if I am allowed to continue being an
adventurer, I have confidence that I will eventually
be able to repay it. \n< Serena >
Of course, that choice is impossible. \n< Man >
However, if that's the case, we have no choice but to
lay our hands on your only asset - your body. \n< Man >
The problem is how to convert it into cash. \n< Man >
Boss. \n< Subordinate >
I understand. \n< Man >
... Adventurer Serena. As a measure against the
losses incurred during this mission, we will strip you
of your status as your own master. \n< Man >
From today onwards, you shall be identified as a
urban slave, and your status as a master shall be
auctioned off to compensate for the losses. \n< Man >
Am I a slave? Owning slaves is supposed to be
forbidden within the kingdom under church law. \n< Serena >
You become a city slave. As long as you are in the
city, your freedom of movement, action, and property
ownership will be restricted. \n< Man >
This is not a forbidden slave of the church. The
similarity in words... oh, now I see. This is not
good... it's a misleading expression. \n< Man >
It may be corrected eventually. But for now, you have
become a city slave. \n< Man >
They are such an unbearable bunch. \n< Serena >
Okay. You can do whatever you want, whether it's
selling slaves or auctions. \n< Serena >
But no matter what title I may hold, I am who I am.
Let us not be like those who keep wolves on a dog's
leash. \n< Serena >
A smart wolf would be satisfied with a dog collar. If
they know that things could get worse. \n< Man >
Take me with you. \n< Man >
Hah! \n< Subordinate >
